@nathanielmanistaatgoogle: i'm using C# 
thanks for your help - i've found appropriate option `Grpc.Core.ChannelOptions.MaxMessageLength` - it works

maybe you know - does max message length limitation exist for `grpc-java` (netty-based)?

If anyone is interested in the NODE solution for this per channel base you can pass as the third argument the following:
`{
            'grpc.max_send_message_length': 8 * 1024 * 1024,
            'grpc.max_receive_message_length': 8 * 1024 * 1024
        }`
